
JustDrawing.js

A less crude drawing widget based on Prototypes.js

Dependencies: 
    - jQuery
    - Prototypes.js (https://github.com/parenparen/Prototypes.js)


Example:

Instantiation:
  <div id="canvas_container_0"></div>
  <script>
    justDrawing = new JustDrawing ({
        container: "#canvas-container-0",
        width: 500,
        height: 500,
    });
  </script>

